videos.description: Condoleezza Rice, Billie Jean King, Steve Kerr, John Elway, Nneka Ogwumike and Lisa Leslie congratulate Tara VanDerveer on breaking the record for the most women's college basketball wins.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Feature (Notable figures honor Tara VanDerveer on NCAA wins record) 2020/12/15

videos.headline: Notable figures honor Tara VanDerveer on NCAA wins record

videos.description: Tara VanDerveer surpasses Pat Summitt for most wins in NCAA women's college basketball (1,099) with a win vs. Pacific, and the Cardinal celebrate the accomplishment.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Tara VanDerveer, Stanford celebrate wins record) 2020/12/15

videos.headline: Tara VanDerveer, Stanford celebrate wins record

videos.description: Tara VanDerveer joins SVP to discuss her coaching milestone, passing Pat Summitt and the challenges of playing during the pandemic. VanDerveer also gives a shout-out to her mom.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (VanDerveer honors Summitt after reaching coaching milestone) 2020/12/15 SVP

videos.headline: VanDerveer honors Summitt after reaching coaching milestone

videos.description: Chiney Ogwumike tells the story of Stanford head coach Tara VanDerveer's rise to the top of women's college basketball.
